snippet.title: Ultimate Godspeed Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A kart racing game with a unique touch.
Take on the role of a god and modify the race tracks, before racing. Use ramps and platforms to build shortcuts and beware black holes and deadly saw blades placed by other players!.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1435750/Ultimate_Godspeed/
Join our Discord for playtests: https://discord.gg/BrvnXvcHp6
